[[Translation:Main/en/Long date in status bar]]
{{en/-}}
A [[Main/en/Advanced Settings|setting]] that changes how the date is displayed in the status bar.

== Description ==
When this patch is activated the status bar will show the day of the month, month and year all the time.<br>
<code>Always show long date in status bar: On</code><br>
[[File:en/LongDateInStatusBar.png|Status bar with long date]]<br><br>
When this patch is deactivated, the status bar will show just the month and year.  The day of the month can be displayed by pausing the game.<br>
<code>Always show long date in status bar: Off</code><br>
[[File:en/ShortDateInStatusBar.png|Normal status bar]]

== Use ==
This feature is enabled by default. Either disable this patch through the [[Main/en/Advanced Settings/Interface#Always show long date in the status bar|configure patches -> interface]] window or use the following syntax in [[Main/en/openttd.cfg]]:
 [patches]
 status_long_date = false

